Problem 25: Use Case Relationships
Overview

Key relationships among use cases in the Passport Automation System were identified to represent dependencies and extensions between system functionalities.

Use Case Relationships

Apply for Passport → includes Upload Documents

Apply for Passport → includes Book Appointment

Track Application Status → includes Send Notifications

Verify Application → extends Approve / Reject Application

Relationship Description
Use Case	Related Use Case	Relationship Type
Apply for Passport	Upload Documents	Include
Apply for Passport	Book Appointment	Include
Track Application Status	Send Notifications	Include
Verify Application	Approve / Reject Application	Extend
Outcome

Clear functional dependencies were established, ensuring better understanding of system flow and interaction between related use cases.
